                    <span>This is basically a reference book to VB.NEt Functions.
<br />
<br />The book is divided into 2 parts.
<br />
<br />Part 1: Gives you A very simplified introduction to VB.NET
<br />and is only 143 small pages.(If you put them together it is only 71 normal page). So do not expect much from this book.
<br />
<br />Part 2: about 400 pages is only a reference to the functions.
<br />
<br />
<br />Button line: 
<br />Do not buy this if:
<br />You want to learn VB.NET throughly.
<br />
<br />Still I bought it, only because at $2.5(I bought it for that price) it is a good deal for an Index book. 
<br />
<br /></span>
                  
